<P>
U.S. District Judge Dickinson Debevoise ruled in Newark, N.J., that two 
insurance companies must pay for an expensive new anti-cancer procedure for a 
man with a bone marrow malignancy. Nicolae Dozsa, 54, of Jefferson Township, 
