<TYPE>
<P>
Full Run 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA050989-0075 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 54603 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 9, 1989, Tuesday, Home Edition 
