<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ryder Sells Unit: Ryder System sold its Long Beach freight-forwarding unit to 
Radix Ventures. The price wasn't disclosed. The unit, Ryder International 
Freight &amp; Customs Service Inc., served the aerospace, automotive, apparel 
and electronic industries from 14 locations in the United States. Its new 
owner, Radix, is a New York-based customs brokerage and freight forwarder. 
</P>
