COMMISSIONER); LEGISLATION -- CALIFORNIA; AUTOMOBILE INSURANCE; FINES; 
LOBBYING; CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; LEGISLATORS; REPUBLICAN PARTY 
(CALIFORNIA) 
</P>
