<P>
BRIEFCASE: WESTERN DIGITAL TO SELL ITS FULL LINE OF PRODUCTS THROUGH 
COMPUTERLAND; 
</P>
<P>
SCIENCE/TECHNOLOGY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By David Olmos, Times Staff Writer 
